releases/0/tender/title: Framework Agreement for Environmental Planning Consultancy
releases/0/tender/description:
The Forestry Commission is inviting tenders for a Framework Agreement that will operate within South England Forest District with the majority of the work expected to be within the Crown Lands of the New Forest. 

The core objective of the framework will be to obtain the necessary consents within the Town and Country Planning Legislation to allow operational work plans to be delivered.  It will also be utilised to support our Planning and Environment Team in the development of Environmental operational plans, stakeholder engagement and securing other Town and Country Planning consents as required.
